      "paragraphId": "ch_2289_p0014",
      "startOffset": 7982205,
      "endOffset": 7982255,
      "summary": "漫天繁星精算阵只有基本攻防威能，亚仙尊级别不到，因此大爱仙尊、巨阳仙尊选择和星宿仙尊交易"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
